{
  "stem": "8370.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the Boger stayed there and looks on us, says, kommando, stop.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We stopped.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He looked on the faces, look on the face.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You, and take me out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I had, in my right hand, I had a cap.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We have to put the cap down when you go through the gate before the SS.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I got this gold coin.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he ordered me, take me out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The kommando is standing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He say me, dress off.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Put that all down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was winter-- cold like hell, but nothing to do.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But it was snow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what I have done, I have put this gold coin into the snow close to my shoe.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I take the shoe off.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He takes the shoe, puts his hand inside if I got nothing in-- no, then jacket and everything.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was naked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then my, I dressed myself again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And slowly, I put the gold coin back in my hand and walk out in the camp and finish.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was-- so I survived.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I brought a gold coin into the camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I, afterwards, I saw the chap after the roll call who gave me this, and we have made some business, you know.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because you could buy-- they have, they worked plenty of civilian in the camp, supervising technical jobs.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And with them, you could make business.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's mean you gave him a money or a piece of jewelry and he brought you bread, you know, or sausage.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Of course, it cost a fortune.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "For example, a half a bottle of vodka costed-- I remember very well-- $15.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So it was very expensive at this time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Anyhow, and the second time-- and this, I wrote a memoir called I was working in a, in a group of making boreholes.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
